Direct/Backstab/Teleport to the empty tile directly above an Enemy within movement range and deal 2 damage. +2 damage if the Enemy has no other Enemies adjacent to it.

Indirect/Opportunity Strikes/If an Enemy adjacent to the Assassin is attacked, the Assassin attacks it for 1 damage. Will trigger Bloodlust if the Assassin is exhausted. Does not cancel Stun.

Passive/Bloodlust/If the Assassin kills a unit, it may act again. May only activate once per turn.